                                                              FastMath.abs(t)));
    final double dt = FastMath.abs(equations.getTime() - t);
    if (dt <= threshold) {
        throw new NumberIsTooSmallException(LocalizedFormats.TOO_SMALL_INTEGRATION_INTERVAL,
                                            dt, threshold, false);
    }

}


